WEBVTT

00:01.176 --> 00:02.903
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:02.903 --> 00:04.638
SO YOU'RE GONNA GO
TO THE PROFESSOR

00:04.638 --> 00:06.807
AND CONVINCE HIM TO
GIVE YOU A MAKEUP TEST.

00:06.807 --> 00:08.709
I THINK YOU SHOULD BE
MY NEW CHIEF OF STAFF.

00:08.709 --> 00:10.544
I WONDER WHAT SHE WOULD THINK
IF SHE KNEW ABOUT

00:10.544 --> 00:12.212
THE SECRET YOU HAVE
WITH YOUR DAUGHTER.

00:12.212 --> 00:14.781
OUR PROBLEM IS NOW
A NONFACTOR.

00:14.781 --> 00:16.617
[ SIREN WAILS ]

00:16.617 --> 00:17.718
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

00:17.718 --> 00:19.520
SHE WON'T BE
BOTHERING YOU AGAIN.

00:19.520 --> 00:21.487
BRO, I TOLD YOU
THIS IS MY SISTER'S CAR.

00:21.487 --> 00:22.689
THAT'S A WHOLE LOT OF COKE.

00:22.689 --> 00:25.391
WHAT DID YOU DO, DAVID?

00:25.391 --> 00:26.459
YOU GOT TO COME DOWN HERE
AND TELL THESE FOLKS

00:26.459 --> 00:27.460
THAT THIS IS
YOUR COCAINE.

00:27.460 --> 00:28.929
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

00:28.929 --> 00:30.531
BENNY'S IN TROUBLE.
HE'S IN JAIL.

00:30.531 --> 00:32.298
‐IN JAIL FOR WHAT?
‐WELL, THAT'S WHAT I ‐‐

00:32.298 --> 00:33.800
MNH‐MNH.
YOU JUST STAY RIGHT THERE.

00:33.800 --> 00:35.301
‐[ CRIES ]
‐COME ON.

00:35.301 --> 00:38.171
[ CRIES ]

00:38.171 --> 00:40.006
HE'S GOING AWAY
FOR A LONG TIME.

00:40.006 --> 00:41.174
WHAT DO YOU MEAN "HE"?

00:41.174 --> 00:43.276
THE PERP THAT WAS
DRIVING THE CAR.

00:43.276 --> 00:44.945
‐IT ISN'T A HE.
‐YES, IT IS.

00:44.945 --> 00:47.080
SHE'S HERE TO SEE THE PERP.
HE'S HER BROTHER.

00:47.080 --> 00:48.649
YOU ARRESTED
THE WRONG PERSON.

00:48.649 --> 00:53.820
♪♪♪♪

00:59.793 --> 01:02.202
I KNOW THAT FACE.

01:02.202 --> 01:03.770
I'M TELLING YOU,
I KNOW THAT WOMAN.

01:03.770 --> 01:06.172
WHAT IS GOING ON?

01:06.172 --> 01:09.208
WHAT'S GOING ON IS YOU'VE
ARRESTED THE WRONG PERSON.

01:09.208 --> 01:11.812
YOU GAVE ME THE MAKE
AND MODEL OF THE CAR.

01:11.812 --> 01:12.846
WE PLANTED THE DRUGS.

01:12.846 --> 01:14.648
OH,
I DON'T NEED TO HEAR THAT.

01:14.648 --> 01:16.082
WHAT DO YOU MEAN YOU DON'T
NEED TO HEAR THAT?

01:16.082 --> 01:17.350
THIS WAS YOUR IDEA.

01:17.350 --> 01:20.320
WHY ARE YOU
TELLING ME THAT NOW?

01:20.320 --> 01:21.221
ARE YOU WIRED?

01:21.221 --> 01:23.089
WILL YOU RELAX?

01:23.089 --> 01:25.759
IF YOU GO DOWN FOR THIS,
I GO DOWN, TOO.

01:25.759 --> 01:28.762
GET YOUR HANDS ‐‐
GET OFF OF ME!

01:28.762 --> 01:31.297
IT'S THE CASES
YOU BROUGHT BEFORE ME

01:31.297 --> 01:34.234
THAT MADE YOU
DETECTIVE.

01:34.234 --> 01:35.702
DON'T YOU FORGET THAT.

01:35.702 --> 01:38.271
WILL YOU LET IT GO,
DAVID?

01:38.271 --> 01:41.908
I SAID I'M CLEAN.

01:41.908 --> 01:44.845
I TOLD YOU
IT WAS A FEMALE.

01:44.845 --> 01:47.447
NO, YOU DIDN'T.

01:47.447 --> 01:49.182
OF COURSE I DID.

01:49.182 --> 01:50.416
DAVID, I WOULD HAVE
KNOWN THE DIFFERENCE

01:50.416 --> 01:52.152
BETWEEN A MALE
AND A FEMALE.

01:52.152 --> 01:54.588
ARE YOU SO STUPID?

01:54.588 --> 01:57.457
YOU RAN THE PROFILE.

01:57.457 --> 01:59.259
WELL, WHO IS THIS KID?

01:59.259 --> 02:02.669
HOW THE HELL DO I KNOW?
YOU'RE THE ONE WHO ARRESTED HIM.

02:02.669 --> 02:04.771
WELL, WHAT DO YOU
WANT US TO DO?

02:08.441 --> 02:10.410
DROP THE CHARGES.

02:12.646 --> 02:14.114
I CAN'T DO THAT.

02:14.114 --> 02:16.049
WHY NOT?

02:16.049 --> 02:18.718
YOU SAID TAKE THIS STRAIGHT UP
TO THE D. A.'S OFFICE,

02:18.718 --> 02:19.819
WHICH I DID.

02:19.819 --> 02:21.922
THAT PART OF THE INSTRUCTIONS
HE FOLLOWS.

02:21.922 --> 02:24.390
SHE HAS IT.
SHE LOOKED AT THE CASE.

02:24.390 --> 02:26.326
SHE SAYS IT'S AIRTIGHT.

02:26.326 --> 02:30.296
YOU FIND A WAY
TO GET THE CHARGES DROPPED.

02:30.296 --> 02:32.065
HOLD ON A SECOND.

02:32.065 --> 02:34.735
YOU ASKED ME TO DO THIS.
IT'S DONE.

02:34.735 --> 02:37.137
I DO. I DON'T UNDO.

02:37.137 --> 02:39.472
YOU DEAL WITH IT.

02:39.472 --> 02:42.042
REMEMBER?

02:42.042 --> 02:43.877
WE ARE EVEN.

02:43.877 --> 02:52.052
♪♪♪♪

02:52.052 --> 02:55.055
