03:01.434 --> 03:04.437
OH, WHAT IS TAKING HIM
SO LONG?

03:08.041 --> 03:09.209
OOH!

03:09.209 --> 03:12.145
CAN'T TOUCH HIM!

03:12.145 --> 03:13.814
LORD JESUS.

03:13.814 --> 03:18.552
EVERYTHING IS ALL RIGHT, MAMA.
I'M GOOD.

03:18.552 --> 03:22.422
WHAT HAPPENED, BABY?
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:22.422 --> 03:24.925
TALK TO ME.

03:24.925 --> 03:26.993
BENNY?

03:26.993 --> 03:33.066
♪♪♪♪

03:33.066 --> 03:34.935
[ SIGHS ]
I WAS ON MY WAY TO GET DARCI,

03:34.935 --> 03:37.470
AND I GOT PULLED OVER,

03:37.470 --> 03:39.039
AND THERE WAS COCAINE
IN THE CAR.

03:39.039 --> 03:43.577
OH...

03:43.577 --> 03:45.912
WHAT WERE YOU DOING WITH
COCAINE IN YOUR TRUCK?

03:45.912 --> 03:47.914
I WASN'T IN MY TRUCK,
MOMMY.

03:47.914 --> 03:57.658
♪♪♪♪

03:57.658 --> 04:00.634
HE WAS DRIVING MY CAR.

04:00.634 --> 04:04.137
WHAT CAR?

04:04.137 --> 04:06.940
I HAVE A NEW CAR.

04:06.940 --> 04:11.211
WHERE'D YOU GET THE MONEY
TO GET A NEW CAR?

04:11.211 --> 04:14.581
YOU SELLING DRUGS NOW?

04:14.581 --> 04:16.817
I'M NOT DEALING DRUGS.

04:16.817 --> 04:21.421
I DON'T KNOW HOW
COCAINE GOT IN MY CAR.

04:21.421 --> 04:23.256
YEAH, YOU DO.

04:23.256 --> 04:25.458
YOU'RE LYING.
GO AND TELL THE TRUTH.

04:25.458 --> 04:26.560
MAMA, CALM DOWN.

04:26.560 --> 04:28.061
NOW YOU SHUT UP.

04:28.061 --> 04:30.196
YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE EVEN
BEEN IN HER CAR.

04:30.196 --> 04:31.932
I TOLD YOU
YOU CAN'T TRUST HER.

04:31.932 --> 04:33.499
SHE WILL SELL YOU
DOWN THE RIVER

04:33.499 --> 04:36.135
IF IT MEANT SOMEBODY
GIVING HER A DOLLAR.

04:36.135 --> 04:41.508
♪♪♪♪

04:41.508 --> 04:43.544
I DIDN'T KNOW.

04:43.544 --> 04:46.747
YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME,
DO YOU, BENNY?

04:46.747 --> 04:48.749
I TOLD YOU
THIS CHILD WAS EVIL.

04:48.749 --> 04:54.187
♪♪♪♪

04:54.187 --> 04:56.523
MAMA, SHE SAYS
SHE DIDN'T KNOW.

04:56.523 --> 04:59.092
YOU DON'T BELIEVE ME?

04:59.092 --> 05:04.337
WATCH AND SEE IF SHE DON'T
LEAVE YOU HANGING.

05:04.337 --> 05:07.107
BENNY,
I WOULDN'T DO THAT.

05:07.107 --> 05:09.142
PROVE IT.

05:11.912 --> 05:13.179
HOW?

05:13.179 --> 05:15.081
GET ON UP FROM HERE,
MARCH IN THERE,

05:15.081 --> 05:16.349
AND TELL THEM PEOPLE
THE TRUTH.

05:16.349 --> 05:20.186
GO ON AND TELL THEM
THAT THOSE WERE YOUR DRUGS.

05:20.186 --> 05:21.454
THEY WEREN'T MINE.

05:21.454 --> 05:23.757
THEN HOW DID THEY GET
IN YOUR CAR?

05:23.757 --> 05:25.091
I DON'T KNOW.

05:25.091 --> 05:27.493
I BET YOU
IF I HAD A DOLLAR,

05:27.493 --> 05:29.362
YOU'D FIND AN ANSWER,
SEE,

05:29.362 --> 05:32.165
'CAUSE ALL YOU CARE ABOUT
IS MONEY AND YOURSELF.

05:32.165 --> 05:34.034
MAMA, PLEASE.

05:34.034 --> 05:37.504
YOU GONNA LET YOUR BROTHER
GO TO JAIL?

05:41.675 --> 05:46.346
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME TO DO,
HMM?

05:46.346 --> 05:52.719
I DON'T KNOW HOW
COCAINE GOT IN MY CAR.

05:52.719 --> 05:55.421
THEN HOW DID YOU
AFFORD THAT CAR?

05:55.421 --> 05:57.490
I SAW IT, CANDACE.

05:57.490 --> 05:59.092
YOU'RE EITHER SELLING DRUGS

05:59.092 --> 06:01.535
OR YOU'RE SELLING
YOUR TRIFLING ASS.

06:01.535 --> 06:05.338
NOW YOU GONNA GET UP AND GO
TELL THEM PEOPLE THE TRUTH.

06:08.809 --> 06:10.944
AND LIKE I TOLD YOU ‐‐

06:10.944 --> 06:12.045
MAMA!

06:12.045 --> 06:13.747
GIRL, DON'T YOU JUMP IN MY FACE
NO MORE!

06:13.747 --> 06:14.848
I AIN'T PLAYING WITH YOU,
CANDACE!

06:14.848 --> 06:16.049
I'VE HAD IT!
‐MA'AM, RELAX!

06:16.049 --> 06:17.818
LISTEN. WHAT YOU GONNA DO,
ARREST ME?

06:17.818 --> 06:19.953
GO ON AND DO IT!
GO ON!

06:19.953 --> 06:21.855
THIS GIRL RIGHT HERE
NEEDS HER BUTT BEAT.

06:21.855 --> 06:24.324
‐MAMA, STOP IT!
‐WHAT?!

06:24.324 --> 06:26.960
EVERYTHING YOU TOUCH YOU RUIN!

06:26.960 --> 06:29.963
IT'S LIKE YOU ARE THE DEVIL,
HUH?

06:29.963 --> 06:32.098
YOU GOT YOUR BROTHER
IN THIS WHOLE SITUATION.

06:32.098 --> 06:34.668
GET OUT, CANDACE!
JUST GET OUT!

06:34.668 --> 06:38.471
OH, NOW YOU GONNA CRY?

06:38.471 --> 06:40.841
PLEASE.

06:40.841 --> 06:44.144
BENNY, LOOK AT ME.

06:44.144 --> 06:45.612
LOOK AT ME, BENNY.

06:45.612 --> 06:48.582
LOOK AT ME.

06:48.582 --> 06:54.220
I DIDN'T KNOW,
BUT I'M GONNA FIX IT, OKAY?

06:54.220 --> 06:55.856
I'M GONNA FIX IT.

06:55.856 --> 06:57.858
THE ONLY THING YOU CAN DO TO
FIX THIS IS GO IN THERE

06:57.858 --> 06:59.926
AND TELL THEM PEOPLE
THE TRUTH.

07:03.136 --> 07:04.370
I DIDN'T KNOW.

07:04.370 --> 07:05.939
GIRL,
GET OUT OF MY FACE.

07:05.939 --> 07:13.714
♪♪♪♪

07:19.052 --> 07:21.054
LORD HAVE MERCY.

07:21.054 --> 07:23.356
I DON'T THINK SHE DID IT, MAMA.
I DON'T THINK SHE KNEW.

07:23.356 --> 07:25.692
BENNY, YOU ACT LIKE
YOU DON'T KNOW YOUR SISTER.

07:25.692 --> 07:26.893
I DO.
I KNOW WHEN SHE'S LYING.

07:26.893 --> 07:28.829
YEAH, SHE'S LYING NOW!

07:32.733 --> 07:34.768
I DON'T THINK SO.

07:34.768 --> 07:38.338
SHE NEED TO GO IN THERE
AND TELL THEM PEOPLE THE TRUTH.

07:38.338 --> 07:39.472
I'M TIRED OF
TALKING ABOUT IT.

07:39.472 --> 07:44.077
I DON'T EVEN WANT TO
TALK ABOUT IT NO MORE.

07:44.077 --> 07:45.912
WHAT ARE WE
SUPPOSED TO DO NOW?

07:45.912 --> 07:49.415
WHAT IS OUR NEXT STEP?

07:49.415 --> 07:51.685
THINK THEY'RE GONNA GIVE ME
A PUBLIC DEFENDER

07:51.685 --> 07:53.820
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT.
‐NO, NO.

07:53.820 --> 07:55.021
WHAT OTHER CHOICE DO WE HAVE,
MAMA?

07:55.021 --> 07:56.156
I'M GONNA
GET YOU A LAWYER.

07:56.156 --> 07:57.457
MAMA,
WE CAN'T AFFORD A LAWYER.

07:57.457 --> 07:59.660
MY HOUSE IS PAID FOR,
REMEMBER?

07:59.660 --> 08:02.368
NO.
I'M NOT DOING THAT, NO.

08:02.368 --> 08:03.670
WELL, I'M NOT
LEAVING YOU IN HERE.

08:03.670 --> 08:05.672
I AIN'T GONNA DO IT!
‐IT'S TIME TO GO.

08:05.672 --> 08:06.873
NO, NO, NO.
I NEED TO ‐‐

08:06.873 --> 08:08.942
CAN I JUST HUG MY BABY?
‐IT'S TIME TO GO, MA'AM.

08:08.942 --> 08:10.143
SHE'S JUST TRYING TO HUG ME,
MAN. IT'S MY MAMA.

08:10.143 --> 08:11.444
‐TIME TO GO!
‐PLEASE!

08:11.444 --> 08:12.679
DON'T WORRY. I LOVE YOU.
EVERYTHING'S GONNA BE FINE.

08:12.679 --> 08:15.481
I LOVE YOU, TOO.
DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME.

08:15.481 --> 08:18.619
I'LL BE ALL RIGHT, BABY.
WE GONNA GET YOU A LAWYER.

08:18.619 --> 08:26.392
♪♪♪♪

08:26.392 --> 08:30.296
MAY NOT BE SUCH A BAD MISTAKE
AFTER ALL.

08:39.873 --> 08:45.579
♪♪♪♪

08:45.579 --> 08:51.384
♪♪♪♪

08:51.384 --> 08:53.787
WELL, WELL, WELL.

08:53.787 --> 08:58.324
LOOK WHO'S LATE FOR HER FIRST
DAY AS CHIEF OF STAFF.

08:58.324 --> 09:00.627
OOH, IS THAT LOOK
SUPPOSED TO SCARE ME?

09:00.627 --> 09:02.435
AIN'T NOBODY TRYING
TO SCARE YOU.

09:02.435 --> 09:06.172
WELL, GOOD,
'CAUSE IT DOESN'T WORK.

09:07.307 --> 09:09.075
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

09:09.075 --> 09:11.011
TO DO MY JOB.

09:11.011 --> 09:12.646
SHE WANTS TEA.

09:12.646 --> 09:15.448
THEN MAKE IT.

09:15.448 --> 09:17.383
OH, SHE WANTS TEA,

09:17.383 --> 09:20.921
AND SHE WANTS YOU TO MAKE IT
AND TAKE IT TO HER.

09:32.833 --> 09:36.169
WHERE'S THE CHAMOMILE?

09:36.169 --> 09:38.104
I DON'T KNOW.

09:38.104 --> 09:40.874
CELINE, YOU KNOW SHE DOESN'T
LIKE ANYTHING BUT CHAMOMILE TEA.

09:40.874 --> 09:44.645
WHERE IS IT?

09:44.645 --> 09:45.746
I DON'T KNOW.

09:45.746 --> 09:47.748
BUT YOU SHOULD KNOW.

09:47.748 --> 09:53.319
♪♪♪♪

09:53.319 --> 09:58.859
♪♪♪♪

09:58.859 --> 10:03.937
IT WAS HERE LAST NIGHT
WHEN I LEFT.

10:03.937 --> 10:07.407
WELL,
MAYBE THEY DRANK IT ALL.

10:07.407 --> 10:10.577
YOU THINK YOU'RE CUTE,
DON'T YOU?

10:10.577 --> 10:12.278
CUTE?

10:12.278 --> 10:13.647
NO, HONEY.

10:13.647 --> 10:15.682
I'M BEAUTIFUL.

10:18.685 --> 10:21.988
WHAT DID I DO TO YOU?

10:21.988 --> 10:26.527
DO YOU HAVE TIME?
BECAUSE THE LIST IS REALLY LONG.

10:26.527 --> 10:29.462
CELINE,
GIVE ME THE TEA.

10:29.462 --> 10:32.866
I DON'T KNOW WHERE IT IS,
HANNA.

10:32.866 --> 10:42.876
♪♪♪♪

10:42.876 --> 10:43.910
I FOUND IT.

10:43.910 --> 10:46.479
I MEAN, YOU'RE TRYING TO
HIDE THE TEA.

10:46.479 --> 10:49.015
I AM NOT
IN THE MOOD FOR THIS.

10:49.015 --> 10:51.017
GOOD FOR YOU.

10:51.017 --> 11:00.026
♪♪♪♪

11:00.026 --> 11:09.042
♪♪♪♪

11:09.042 --> 11:13.179
WHERE'S THE HONEY?

11:13.179 --> 11:15.015
NO SE.

11:15.015 --> 11:16.850
YOU KNOW,
T‐THIS IS CHILDISH,

11:16.850 --> 11:18.051
AND THIS IS DAMN STUPID.

11:18.051 --> 11:20.587
OOH, OOH!
SUCH LANGUAGE.

11:23.123 --> 11:25.025
FINE.

11:25.025 --> 11:26.593
I WILL GO UP THERE AND TELL HER

11:26.593 --> 11:27.894
YOU TRIED TO HIDE THE TEA
AND THE HONEY.

11:27.894 --> 11:32.232
FINE.

11:32.232 --> 11:34.768
I AM NOT
IN THE MOOD FOR THIS.

11:34.768 --> 11:36.803
OKAY, FINE. HERE.

11:41.542 --> 11:43.143
GOD, YOU ARE CRAZY.

11:43.143 --> 11:44.377
NO.

11:44.377 --> 11:46.146
NO,
YOU KNOW WHAT'S CRAZY?

11:46.146 --> 11:49.015
IF I WERE YOU
OR ANYTHING LIKE YOU,

11:49.015 --> 11:51.852
I WOULD MISUSE ALL MY FRIENDS
AND STEP ON THEM

11:51.852 --> 11:53.687
IN ORDER TO
GET FURTHER IN LIFE.

11:53.687 --> 11:56.156
BUT I'M NOT YOU.

11:56.156 --> 12:01.367
YOU ARE AWFUL.

12:01.367 --> 12:04.004
OOH!

12:04.004 --> 12:05.672
I HAVE
HAD ENOUGH OF YOU.

12:05.672 --> 12:09.209
MM‐HMM.

12:09.209 --> 12:14.180
WAIT. ACTUALLY ‐‐
NO, NO, SHE DIDN'T SAY TEA.

12:14.180 --> 12:16.717
I‐I THINK
SHE WANTS COFFEE.

12:32.098 --> 12:34.134
[ LAUGHS ]

12:38.238 --> 12:40.206
THERE YOU ARE.

12:40.206 --> 12:42.943
YOU'VE BEEN HERE A WHILE NOW
AND HAVEN'T BEEN LATE ONCE,

12:42.943 --> 12:45.045
NOT EVEN
IN THAT STORM WE HAD.

12:45.045 --> 12:46.146
I'M SORRY I'M LATE.

12:46.146 --> 12:47.914
IT'S NOT A PROBLEM.

12:47.914 --> 12:49.249
ARE YOU OKAY?

12:49.249 --> 12:51.117
YES, THANK YOU.

12:51.117 --> 12:52.719
DID YOU TAKE YOUR MEDICINE?

12:52.719 --> 12:54.154
I'M OUT OF IT.

12:54.154 --> 12:56.389
I JUST FILLED IT
YESTERDAY.

12:56.389 --> 12:58.458
I'M NOT TALKING
ABOUT THAT.

12:58.458 --> 13:02.268
I'M TALKING ABOUT
THE GRASS.

13:02.268 --> 13:04.137
OH, I SEE
YOU DON'T FEEL LIKE SMILING.

13:04.137 --> 13:08.408
WHAT'S GOING ON?

13:08.408 --> 13:09.543
HANNA?

13:09.543 --> 13:11.044
MA'AM.

13:11.044 --> 13:13.514
WHAT IS THE MATTER?

13:13.514 --> 13:18.184
MRS. CRYER, DO YOU KNOW A LAWYER
I MIGHT BE ABLE TO HIRE?

13:18.184 --> 13:20.887
WHAT IS GOING ON?

13:20.887 --> 13:23.056
I'M HAVING FAMILY PROBLEMS,

13:23.056 --> 13:24.658
AND I NEED A LAWYER.

13:24.658 --> 13:27.393
WHAT KIND OF PROBLEMS?

13:27.393 --> 13:29.462
I'D RATHER NOT SAY.

13:29.462 --> 13:33.734
OKAY, WELL, DO YOU KNOW WHAT
KIND OF ATTORNEY YOU NEED?

13:33.734 --> 13:35.235
CRIMINAL, I THINK.

13:35.235 --> 13:39.706
‐CRIMINAL?!
‐YES.

13:39.706 --> 13:42.709
IS THIS CRIMINAL ATTORNEY
FOR YOU?

13:42.709 --> 13:45.178
NO ‐‐ YES ‐‐

13:45.178 --> 13:48.148
W‐WELL, NOT FOR ME.

13:48.148 --> 13:50.350
DO YOU KNOW OF ANYONE?

13:50.350 --> 13:52.919
I THINK SO.

13:52.919 --> 13:55.055
THANK YOU.

13:55.055 --> 13:57.824
IS EVERYTHING OKAY?

13:57.824 --> 14:00.360
IT'S GONNA BE FINE.

14:00.360 --> 14:04.905
HANNA...

14:04.905 --> 14:06.507
YOU HAVE BEEN THERE FOR ME

14:06.507 --> 14:08.909
THROUGH THIS CANCER.

14:08.909 --> 14:10.511
LET ME BE THERE FOR YOU.

14:10.511 --> 14:11.645
NO, I'M FINE.

14:11.645 --> 14:12.913
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

14:12.913 --> 14:14.681
YOU'RE SHAKING
LIKE A LEAF!

14:14.681 --> 14:17.183
WELL, THIS IS AN AWKWARD
SITUATION, MRS. CRYER.

14:17.183 --> 14:18.919
I MEAN, YOU'RE MY BOSS.

14:18.919 --> 14:22.823
AND I‐I DON'T WANT ANY FAVORS
FROM YOU.

14:22.823 --> 14:25.025
I‐I DON'T WANT TO
GET THESE LINES CROSSED.

14:25.025 --> 14:27.528
CUT THE CRAP! THE LINES
ARE ALREADY CROSSED, HANNA.

14:27.528 --> 14:30.564
WHAT IS IT?

14:30.564 --> 14:35.235
ALL I NEED IS
THE NAME OF A LAWYER.

14:35.235 --> 14:37.571
OKAY.

14:37.571 --> 14:40.941
SHUT ME OUT.

14:40.941 --> 14:43.877
BUT YOU'RE COMING WITH ME.

14:43.877 --> 14:45.646
WHERE ARE WE GOING?

14:45.646 --> 14:47.881
YOU CAN'T WORK LIKE THIS.

14:47.881 --> 14:50.951
OBVIOUSLY
THIS IS SERIOUS.

14:50.951 --> 14:52.786
WE'RE GONNA
PAY JIM A VISIT.

14:52.786 --> 14:54.655
GO GET YOUR PURSE.

14:54.655 --> 14:56.657
OKAY.

14:56.657 --> 15:06.072
♪♪♪♪

15:06.072 --> 15:15.481
♪♪♪♪

15:15.481 --> 15:19.185
HOW ARE YOU?

15:19.185 --> 15:23.323
I'M FINE.

15:23.323 --> 15:28.529
BENNY, YOU KNOW
I DIDN'T DO THIS.

15:28.529 --> 15:30.564
YEAH, I KNOW.

15:35.602 --> 15:37.638
I AM SO SORRY.

15:40.974 --> 15:44.177
WHERE'D YOU GET THAT CAR
FROM?

15:44.177 --> 15:46.012
THE GUY I WAS TELLING YOU
ABOUT?

15:46.012 --> 15:47.614
MM‐HMM.

15:47.614 --> 15:48.949
HE GAVE IT TO ME.

15:48.949 --> 15:52.385
YOU SURE
HE DIDN'T DO THIS?

15:52.385 --> 15:54.387
YOU SURE
HE DIDN'T SET YOU UP?

15:54.387 --> 15:59.259
♪♪♪♪

15:59.259 --> 16:00.727
[ SIGHS ]

16:00.727 --> 16:03.904
CANDACE, HOW DEEP INTO THIS
ARE YOU?

16:03.904 --> 16:06.973
PRETTY DEEP...

16:06.973 --> 16:08.875
AND ABOUT TO GET DEEPER.

16:08.875 --> 16:11.945
MAKE SURE YOU THINK BEFORE
YOU DO ANYTHING, OKAY?

16:11.945 --> 16:13.079
DON'T DO NOTHING CRAZY.

16:13.079 --> 16:15.181
DON'T BE STUPID.

16:15.181 --> 16:18.585
I GOT THIS.

16:18.585 --> 16:22.155
[ SIGHS ]

16:22.155 --> 16:24.157
NO TOUCHING, MA'AM.

16:24.157 --> 16:31.364
♪♪♪♪

16:31.364 --> 16:32.933
I LOVE YOU.

16:32.933 --> 16:34.535
I LOVE YOU.

16:34.535 --> 16:36.503
BE CAREFUL.

16:43.009 --> 16:48.114
♪♪♪♪

16:48.114 --> 16:53.186
♪♪♪♪

16:53.186 --> 16:54.821
HELLO.

16:54.821 --> 16:56.690
WELL...

16:56.690 --> 17:00.794
AND TO WHAT DO I OWE
THE PRESSURE OF YOUR COMPANY?

17:00.794 --> 17:04.070
CAN'T A WOMAN
COME VISIT HER HUSBAND?

17:04.070 --> 17:05.238
CERTAINLY.

17:05.238 --> 17:06.239
HANNA.

17:06.239 --> 17:08.174
HELLO, MR. CRYER.

17:08.174 --> 17:09.576
SO WHAT'S UP?

17:09.576 --> 17:11.512
HANNA HAS AN ISSUE.

17:11.512 --> 17:14.447
SHE WON'T TELL ME WHAT IT IS,
BUT IT'S SERIOUS.

17:14.447 --> 17:17.818
SHE NEEDS AN ATTORNEY.

17:17.818 --> 17:19.219
WHAT KIND?

17:19.219 --> 17:21.254
CRIMINAL.

17:25.058 --> 17:27.661
HANNA, IT WOULD BE
VERY HELPFUL TO ME

17:27.661 --> 17:30.063
IF YOU WOULD TELL ME
EXACTLY WHAT'S GOING ON?

17:32.899 --> 17:35.569
MY SON IS IN TROUBLE.

17:35.569 --> 17:37.470
OH, DEAR.

17:37.470 --> 17:41.942
WE ALL KNOW
ABOUT THAT.

17:41.942 --> 17:44.878
HE DIDN'T DO IT.

17:44.878 --> 17:49.115
WHAT KIND OF TROUBLE,
HANNA?

17:49.115 --> 17:50.517
DRUGS.

17:50.517 --> 17:51.685
AH.

17:51.685 --> 17:55.021
HE WAS DRIVING MY DAUGHTER'S CAR
AND GOT ARRESTED.

17:59.325 --> 18:01.668
WOULD YOU MIND GIVING
KATHERYN AND I

18:01.668 --> 18:04.204
JUST A FEW MINUTES IN PRIVATE,
PLEASE?

18:04.204 --> 18:06.940
‐SURE.
‐THANK YOU.

18:11.878 --> 18:13.714
OKAY. WHAT IS IT?

18:13.714 --> 18:15.281
SO WE'RE TAKING ON PROJECTS
NOW?

18:15.281 --> 18:17.017
I BEG YOUR PARDON.

18:17.017 --> 18:18.785
YOU KNOW THIS IS
A NEVER‐ENDING CYCLE, RIGHT?

18:18.785 --> 18:20.020
I MEAN, WE HELP HER ONCE,

18:20.020 --> 18:21.722
WE'RE GONNA HELP HER OVER
AND OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

18:21.722 --> 18:24.124
IT'S NEVER GONNA STOP.
‐SHE'S NOT THAT WAY.

18:24.124 --> 18:25.592
I THOUGHT YOU AND I
HAD AN UNDERSTANDING

18:25.592 --> 18:27.027
WE'RE GONNA KEEP THE HELP
AT AN ARM'S LENGTH,

18:27.027 --> 18:29.129
ESPECIALLY AFTER THAT OTHER
LITTLE INCIDENT.

18:29.129 --> 18:31.164
[ SCOFFS ] NOW, WHICH INCIDENT
WOULD THAT BE?

18:31.164 --> 18:32.533
THAT WOULD BE THE ONE
WHERE YOU SAID

18:32.533 --> 18:34.400
THAT THE GARDENER
WAS JUST LIKE FAMILY

18:34.400 --> 18:36.202
UNTIL I HAD TO WRITE HIM A CHECK
EVERY MONTH.

18:36.202 --> 18:38.138
JIM, SHE IS NOT
ASKING FOR MONEY.

18:38.138 --> 18:39.873
SHE JUST NEEDS A LAWYER.

18:39.873 --> 18:42.108
ND WHO EXACTLY IS GOING TO
BE PAYING FOR THAT LAWYER?

18:42.108 --> 18:44.678
‐JUST GET THE DAMN LAWYER!
‐YOU KNOW ‐‐

18:44.678 --> 18:47.781
NOW!

18:47.781 --> 18:49.315
DIAL!

18:55.388 --> 18:57.624
DAVID, WOULD YOU MIND
COMING INTO MY OFFICE

18:57.624 --> 18:58.759
FOR A FEW MOMENTS?

18:58.759 --> 19:00.967
THERE'S A DOG I NEED TO
PUT ON A LEASH.

19:00.967 --> 19:03.236
THANK YOU.

19:03.236 --> 19:06.740
THAT DIDN'T HURT NOW,
DID IT?

19:06.740 --> 19:10.076
HANNA, CAN YOU COME BACK IN,
PLEASE?

19:14.214 --> 19:15.248
HELLO, DAVID.

19:15.248 --> 19:17.518
HELLO, KATHERYN.

19:17.518 --> 19:19.786
YOU REMEMBER
OUR MAID HANNA?

19:19.786 --> 19:24.290
UH, YES, I DO.

19:24.290 --> 19:26.392
SHE'S IN NEED OF
A CRIMINAL ATTORNEY.

19:26.392 --> 19:28.629
HER SON IS IN TROUBLE.

19:28.629 --> 19:30.063
WHAT KIND OF TROUBLE?

19:30.063 --> 19:31.197
DRUGS.

19:31.197 --> 19:33.199
BUT HE DIDN'T DO IT.

19:33.199 --> 19:35.235
I KNOW MY SON,
AND THIS IS NOT HIM.

19:35.235 --> 19:36.837
IT'S MY DAUGHTER.

19:36.837 --> 19:39.439
SHE HAS SOME KIND OF
NEW SPORTS CAR,

19:39.439 --> 19:40.874
AND I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHERE SHE GOT IT FROM,

19:40.874 --> 19:44.578
BUT THEY FOUND DRUGS
UNDER THE SEAT.

19:46.212 --> 19:48.148
CAN YOU HELP HER?

19:48.148 --> 19:51.084
KATHERYN, YOU KNOW I'M NO LONGER
A PRACTICING ATTORNEY.

19:51.084 --> 19:53.987
I'M A JUDGE NOW.

19:53.987 --> 19:55.622
I KNOW THAT.

19:55.622 --> 19:58.324
YOUR WIFE REMINDS ME OF IT
ALL THE TIME.

19:58.324 --> 20:01.467
BUT DO YOU THINK YOU CAN FIND
SOMEONE WHO CAN HELP HER?

20:07.073 --> 20:09.843
YES.
YES, I CAN MAKE A FEW CALLS.

20:09.843 --> 20:13.479
THANK YOU SO MUCH.

20:13.479 --> 20:15.348
WELL?

20:15.348 --> 20:17.383
OH, YOU'D LIKE ME TO
DO IT NOW?

20:17.383 --> 20:18.384
YES.

20:18.384 --> 20:20.687
HER SON
IS SITTING IN JAIL.

20:20.687 --> 20:23.890
I'LL GET RIGHT ON IT AS SOON
AS I GET BACK TO MY OFFICE,

20:23.890 --> 20:28.128
BUT, UH, I NEED A FEW MOMENTS
WITH YOUR HUSBAND FIRST.

20:30.396 --> 20:34.601
ALL RIGHT.
BUT MAKE IT SOON.

20:34.601 --> 20:36.737
I'LL SEE YOU LATER,
DARLING.

20:36.737 --> 20:38.004
GOODBYE, SWEETHEART.

20:38.004 --> 20:40.040
LET'S GO, HANNA.

20:47.147 --> 20:49.249
SHE'S A PIECE OF WORK.
ISN'T SHE?

20:49.249 --> 20:50.884
I WANT YOU TO STAND HERE
AND TELL ME

20:50.884 --> 20:52.719
THAT YOU DIDN'T
HAVE A HAND IN THIS.

20:52.719 --> 20:54.988
TELL ME YOU HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH IT.

20:54.988 --> 20:56.657
I CAN'T DO THAT.

20:56.657 --> 20:58.759
BUT I DO HAVE SOMETHING
IMPORTANT TO TELL YOU.

20:58.759 --> 21:00.393
[ SIGHS ]
YOU'VE GOT GOT NOTHING TO SAY

21:00.393 --> 21:02.936
THAT I WANT TO HEAR UNTIL
YOU TELL ME WHAT YOU DID.

21:02.936 --> 21:05.038
I TOOK CARE OF OUR PROBLEM,

21:05.038 --> 21:07.107
BUT YOU HAVE ANOTHER ONE
I DIDN'T SEE COMING.

21:07.107 --> 21:08.709
DAMN IT, DAVID,
WHAT DID YOU DO?

21:08.709 --> 21:09.843
WHAT?

21:09.843 --> 21:13.246
I HAVE A FRIEND IN NARCOTICS
WHO OWED ME A FAVOR.

21:13.246 --> 21:16.950
SO YOU PLANTED EVIDENCE
IN A CAR?

21:16.950 --> 21:19.085
YES.

21:19.085 --> 21:21.087
WHY WOULD YOU DO THAT?

21:21.087 --> 21:25.458
WELL, I HOPE YOU'D HAVE DONE
THE SAME FOR ME.

21:25.458 --> 21:27.060
WHAT DOES THAT
EVEN MEAN?

21:27.060 --> 21:29.195
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

21:29.195 --> 21:32.966
YOU'RE MY FRIEND,
AND I'M WATCHING YOU FALL APART.

21:32.966 --> 21:36.069
I CAN'T DO IT ANYMORE.

21:36.069 --> 21:38.605
YOU HAVEN'T BEEN THE SAME
SINCE YOU TURNED 50.

21:38.605 --> 21:39.673
OH, GOD.

21:39.673 --> 21:41.441
YOU'RE INVOLVED
WITH A WHORE.

21:41.441 --> 21:45.111
WOULD YOU JUST KEEP YOUR
VOICE QUIET, ALL RIGHT?

21:45.111 --> 21:47.848
IN THE PAST, AT LEAST
YOU HAD THE DECENCY

21:47.848 --> 21:49.516
TO KEEP YOUR AFFAIRS
DISCREET.

21:49.516 --> 21:51.518
NOW I DON'T KNOW
WHAT'S GOTTEN INTO YOU.

21:51.518 --> 21:52.753
YOU'VE LOST IT.

21:52.753 --> 21:54.988
DAVID,
WHAT YOU DID WAS WRONG.

21:54.988 --> 21:56.690
YOU SHOULD NOT
HAVE DONE IT.

21:56.690 --> 21:58.291
WHY DO YOU CARE?

21:58.291 --> 21:59.960
‐WHY DO I CARE?
‐I HANDLED THE SITUATION.

21:59.960 --> 22:02.468
WE'VE GOT HER RIGHT WHERE
WE WANT HER.

22:02.468 --> 22:05.138
YOU'RE NOT MAKING ANY SENSE.
CANDACE WAS NOT ARRESTED.

22:05.138 --> 22:07.473
I KNOW, AND I HAD NO IDEA
WHO WAS GONNA BE IN THAT CAR.

22:07.473 --> 22:10.276
SO WHAT YOU DID IS YOU FRAMED ‐‐
YOU FRAMED ‐‐

22:10.276 --> 22:13.614
HEAR ME OUT ‐‐ YOU FRAMED
AN INNOCENT KID,

22:13.614 --> 22:15.516
AND YOU'RE PROUD OF IT.
‐JAMES CRYER...

22:15.516 --> 22:17.784
‐WHAT?
‐...WHO ARE YOU?

22:17.784 --> 22:19.886
THIS HAS GOT TO BE
MORE THAN A MIDLIFE CRISIS.

22:19.886 --> 22:21.354
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHO YOU ARE.

22:21.354 --> 22:26.392
AFTER ALL THESE YEARS,
I DON'T KNOW YOU.

22:26.392 --> 22:30.063
DAVID,
WHAT YOU DID WAS WRONG.

22:30.063 --> 22:31.497
IT'S NOT LIKE YOU.

22:31.497 --> 22:32.733
DO YOU NEED MY HELP
WITH SOMETHING?

22:32.733 --> 22:34.234
I HOPE TO GOD YOU'D HAVE DONE
THE SAME THING

22:34.234 --> 22:35.602
IF I WAS ACTING
THE WAY THAT YOU'RE ACTING.

22:35.602 --> 22:36.637
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

22:36.637 --> 22:38.104
WE ARE TALKING ABOUT
A COMMON STREET WHORE.

22:38.104 --> 22:39.906
BUT THAT DOES NOT
GIVE YOU THE RIGHT

22:39.906 --> 22:41.742
TO PLANT DRUGS
IN SOME KID'S CAR.

22:41.742 --> 22:43.610
YOU ARE ONE OF MANY.
YOU ARE A JOHN.

22:43.610 --> 22:45.879
NO, NO, NO!
IT'S DIFFERENT WITH HER AND ME.

22:45.879 --> 22:47.380
HOW IS IT ‐‐
OH, IT'S DIFFERENT.

22:47.380 --> 22:49.015
‐YES!
‐YOU LOVE HER.

22:49.015 --> 22:50.316
JUST SAY IT.
‐NO.

22:50.316 --> 22:52.318
‐SAY IT.
‐I ‐‐ NO, DAVID, I DON'T.

22:52.318 --> 22:53.587
‐YOU DON'T LOVE HER?
‐NO, I DON'T LOVE HER.

22:53.587 --> 22:54.755
THEN WHY DOES IT MATTER?

22:54.755 --> 22:57.157
WHY DO YOU CARE HOW I HANDLED
THIS SITUATION?

22:57.157 --> 22:58.725
BECAUSE WHAT YOU DID
WAS WRONG.

22:58.725 --> 23:01.434
YOU WERE MARKED.
THEY PLAYED YOU LIKE A BAD HAND.

23:01.434 --> 23:03.504
THEY PLAYED ME LIKE ‐‐
WHO ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

23:03.504 --> 23:06.072
WHO IS "THEY"?

23:06.072 --> 23:07.708
YOU REALLY HAVE NO IDEA?

23:07.708 --> 23:11.377
NO, I HAVE NO IDEA.
WHY DON'T YOU EXPLAIN IT TO ME?

23:11.377 --> 23:12.513
WHAT HAS HAPPENED TO YOU?

23:12.513 --> 23:13.947
YOU ARE IN A HAZE.

23:13.947 --> 23:16.316
A COUPLE YEARS AGO, YOU'D HAVE
SEEN THIS COMING A MILE OFF.

23:16.316 --> 23:18.284
WHAT WOULD I HAVE SEEN COMING
A MILE OFF?

23:18.284 --> 23:19.520
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

23:19.520 --> 23:22.388
HANNA, YOUR MAID WHO WORKS
IN YOUR HOUSE.

23:22.388 --> 23:23.590
YES,
THE MAID THAT I PAY.

23:23.590 --> 23:28.194
HER SON WAS ARRESTED IN
HIS SISTER'S CAR FOR DRUGS.

23:28.194 --> 23:30.931
EXACTLY.

23:30.931 --> 23:34.801
CANDACE'S CAR.

23:34.801 --> 23:38.338
HANNA
IS CANDACE'S MOTHER.

23:40.106 --> 23:42.543
THIS WAS A FAMILY PLAN.

23:42.543 --> 23:45.045
THEY SET YOU UP.

23:45.045 --> 23:46.980
GET YOUR HEAD
OUT OF THE CLOUDS.

23:53.153 --> 24:01.101
♪♪♪♪

24:01.101 --> 24:09.109
♪♪♪♪

24:09.109 --> 24:10.243
TEA?

24:10.243 --> 24:12.145
[ SCOFFS ]

24:12.145 --> 24:16.316
I'M YOUR MAID.
YOU SHOULDN'T BE MAKING ME TEA.

24:16.316 --> 24:19.820
YOU'RE ALSO MY FRIEND.

24:19.820 --> 24:22.455
THANK YOU.

24:22.455 --> 24:24.057
ALTHOUGH
WITH OUR CHILDREN,

24:24.057 --> 24:27.728
YOU SHOULD BE
DRINKING BOURBON.

24:27.728 --> 24:29.730
PRAYING ‐‐

24:29.730 --> 24:32.465
THAT'S WHAT
WE SHOULD BE DOING.

24:32.465 --> 24:34.300
WELL, THAT...

24:34.300 --> 24:36.336
AND DRINKING.

24:39.172 --> 24:41.341
HE'S NEVER BEEN MORE THAN
A HUNDRED YARDS FROM ME

24:41.341 --> 24:44.878
IN HIS WHOLE LIFE.

24:44.878 --> 24:46.446
CALLED HIMSELF
"BEING INDEPENDENT"

24:46.446 --> 24:48.682
AND MOVED
AROUND THE CORNER.

24:48.682 --> 24:52.418
SAID HE WAS TRYING TO
KEEP AN EYE ON ME.

24:52.418 --> 24:56.256
BUT I KNOW
IT WAS JUST TO BE CLOSE.

24:56.256 --> 24:58.224
HE'S A GOOD BOY.

24:58.224 --> 25:02.536
HE'S GOT A GOOD SOUL,
YOU KNOW?

25:02.536 --> 25:06.472
HOW DID HE
GET IN THIS MESS?

25:06.472 --> 25:08.709
WELL,
AS GOOD AS BENNY IS,

25:08.709 --> 25:11.845
MY DAUGHTER
IS THE EXACT OPPOSITE.

25:11.845 --> 25:15.315
SHE GOT HIM INTO IT.

25:15.315 --> 25:18.184
AND I DON'T KNOW WHERE
I WENT WRONG WITH HER.

25:18.184 --> 25:21.154
SOMETIMES IT'S NOT YOU
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

25:21.154 --> 25:24.691
I DID EVERYTHING BY THE BOOK
WITH WYATT.

25:24.691 --> 25:26.893
DID YOU
TAKE HIM TO CHURCH?

25:26.893 --> 25:28.394
YES, I DID,
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

25:28.394 --> 25:30.196
NO,
I'M NOT JUDGING YOU.

25:30.196 --> 25:31.732
I WAS JUST ASKING 'CAUSE I ‐‐

25:31.732 --> 25:35.468
I TOOK BENNY TO CHURCH
EVERY SUNDAY.

25:35.468 --> 25:39.205
AND NOW
HE CAN'T STAND TO GO.

25:39.205 --> 25:41.908
BUT THE BIBLE SAYS,

25:41.908 --> 25:45.245
"TRAIN UP A CHILD IN THE WAY
THAT YOU WOULD HAVE THEM TO GO,

25:45.245 --> 25:48.749
AND WHEN THEY ARE OLDER,
THEY WILL NOT DEPART FROM IT."

25:50.817 --> 25:54.755
MAYBE
HE'LL FIND HIS WAY BACK.

25:54.755 --> 25:57.958
MAYBE WYATT WILL, TOO.

25:57.958 --> 25:59.993
THAT'S WHERE
IT ALL STARTED.

26:03.570 --> 26:07.040
THE PRIEST WAS HAVING A RETREAT
FOR THE BOYS AT THE PARISH.

26:07.040 --> 26:09.643
WYATT DIDN'T WANT TO GO.

26:09.643 --> 26:11.678
HE DIDN'T...

26:15.181 --> 26:17.718
ENOUGH OF THAT.

26:17.718 --> 26:21.522
IF THIS CANCER DOESN'T KILL ME,
THE MEMORY OF THAT WILL.

26:24.457 --> 26:27.861
HE WAS OUT OF MY SIGHT
FOR ONE SUMMER,

26:27.861 --> 26:29.563
AND EVERYTHING CHANGED.

26:31.765 --> 26:33.800
WHAT HAPPENED?

26:36.637 --> 26:40.774
IT'S STILL TOO PAINFUL
TO TALK ABOUT.

26:40.774 --> 26:42.509
HAVE YOU EVER TRIED
TALKING TO HER?

26:42.509 --> 26:44.377
WHO? MY DAUGHTER?

26:44.377 --> 26:45.478
YES.

26:45.478 --> 26:47.914
[ SCOFFS ] YES,
TILL I'M BLUE IN THE FACE.

26:47.914 --> 26:52.352
SHE JUST DOESN'T GET IT.

26:52.352 --> 26:56.189
I MEAN
REALLY TALKING TO HER.

26:56.189 --> 26:59.526
AND YOU SHOULD KNOW
THAT LISTENING

26:59.526 --> 27:04.470
IS JUST AS IMPORTANT
AS TALKING.

27:04.470 --> 27:08.174
AND YOU'D BE SURPRISED HOW MANY
THINGS PEOPLE TELL YOU

27:08.174 --> 27:11.878
WHEN THEY ARE TRYING NOT
TO TELL YOU TOO MUCH.

27:11.878 --> 27:15.749
I CAN'T STAND TO BE
AROUND HER RIGHT NOW.

27:15.749 --> 27:17.751
WELL,
WHEN YOU'RE READY ‐‐

27:17.751 --> 27:20.453
AND YOU'RE GONNA NEED
TO BE READY SOON,

27:20.453 --> 27:23.857
BECAUSE YOU'RE GONNA NEED TO
KNOW ALL YOU CAN FROM HER

27:23.857 --> 27:27.293
IN ORDER TO HELP YOUR SON.

27:27.293 --> 27:29.730
SHE LIES
WHEN THE TRUTH WILL DO.

27:29.730 --> 27:32.198
WELL, YOU KNOW YOUR CHILD.
I DON'T.

27:32.198 --> 27:34.968
IT'S JUST MY SUGGESTION.

27:34.968 --> 27:37.137
THANK YOU.

27:37.137 --> 27:38.739
I HEAR YOU.

27:38.739 --> 27:42.543
BUT I DON'T KNOW IF I CAN
TALK TO HER RIGHT NOW.

27:42.543 --> 27:44.578
FOR YOUR SON?

27:47.614 --> 27:51.484
FOR MY SON, BENNY.

27:53.920 --> 27:55.689
OH, LORD.

27:55.689 --> 27:58.859
HANNA,
I KNOW YOU'RE WORRIED,

27:58.859 --> 28:02.569
BUT EVERYTHING'S
GOING TO BE FINE.

28:02.569 --> 28:04.805
HOW DO YOU KNOW?

28:04.805 --> 28:07.340
I KNOW. TRUST ME.

28:10.443 --> 28:12.979
THANK YOU.

28:12.979 --> 28:15.448
DON'T MENTION IT.

28:15.448 --> 28:18.819
HANNA...

28:18.819 --> 28:20.821
I AM ALWAYS HERE FOR YOU.

28:20.821 --> 28:27.127
♪♪♪♪

28:27.127 --> 28:29.495
I BETTER BE
GETTING ON HOME.

28:29.495 --> 28:33.199
OKAY.
TRY NOT TO STRESS OUT TOO MUCH.

28:33.199 --> 28:35.435
MM‐HMM.

28:35.435 --> 28:38.872
AND YOU TRY TO GET SOME REST,
TOO.

28:38.872 --> 28:41.474
YOU GOT TO SEE THE DOCTOR
TOMORROW.

28:41.474 --> 28:43.076
[ GROANS ]
THAT AGAIN.

28:43.076 --> 28:45.311
THAT AGAIN.
[ SIGHS ]

28:45.311 --> 28:48.481
IT'S CHEMO DAY.

28:48.481 --> 28:51.952
AND IT'S ALSO
JOINT DAY.

28:51.952 --> 28:56.489
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:56.489 --> 29:00.293
THANK YOU, MRS. CRYER.

29:00.293 --> 29:03.670
NO, HANNA, THANK YOU.

29:06.573 --> 29:07.741
GOOD NIGHT.

29:07.741 --> 29:09.776
GOOD NIGHT.

29:24.224 --> 29:26.026
I DIDN'T KNOW
YOU WERE HERE.

29:26.026 --> 29:27.761
I AM HERE.

29:27.761 --> 29:30.564
HOW LONG
HAVE YOU BEEN HERE?

29:30.564 --> 29:32.966
LONG ENOUGH.

29:32.966 --> 29:35.135
REALLY?

29:35.135 --> 29:37.137
REALLY.

29:37.137 --> 29:38.672
WHO WAS THAT?

29:38.672 --> 29:40.974
HANNA.
SHE JUST LEFT.

29:40.974 --> 29:44.244
SHE'S HERE AWFULLY LATE,
ISN'T SHE?

29:44.244 --> 29:46.279
SHE'S WORRIED
ABOUT HER SON.

29:49.115 --> 29:51.952
THANK YOU
FOR HELPING HER.

29:51.952 --> 29:55.221
YOU'RE WELCOME.

29:55.221 --> 29:57.357
HOW WELL
DO YOU KNOW HANNA?

29:57.357 --> 30:02.102
AS WELL AS YOU CAN KNOW A PERSON
IN A SHORT AMOUNT OF TIME.

30:02.102 --> 30:04.137
SHE'S GOOD‐HEARTED.

30:04.137 --> 30:05.939
HMM.

30:05.939 --> 30:08.408
YOU NEVER ASKED ME
WHAT I THOUGHT ABOUT HER.

30:08.408 --> 30:11.277
WHEN HAVE YOU EVER CARED
ABOUT THE STAFF ‐‐

30:11.277 --> 30:14.114
OR THE STAFF OVER 30?

30:14.114 --> 30:15.982
I RESENT THAT.

30:15.982 --> 30:18.284
YOU WALKED RIGHT INTO THAT,
DARLING.

30:18.284 --> 30:21.688
I WASN'T THE ONE SLEEPING WITH
THE POOL MAN'S DAUGHTER.

30:21.688 --> 30:24.457
YOU WERE.

30:24.457 --> 30:26.226
RIGHT.

30:26.226 --> 30:29.229
WHAT YOU NEED TO DO
IN THE FUTURE

30:29.229 --> 30:30.897
IS YOU NEED TO RUN
A THOROUGH BACKGROUND CHECK

30:30.897 --> 30:32.899
ON ANYONE THAT YOU INVITE
INTO THIS HOUSE.

30:32.899 --> 30:34.901
I CHECKED HER OUT.

30:34.901 --> 30:36.136
WHAT HAS GOTTEN INTO YOU?

30:36.136 --> 30:37.370
NOTHING.

30:37.370 --> 30:39.806
OH, NO, SOMETHING HAS.

30:39.806 --> 30:42.509
WHY ALL THIS INTEREST
IN WHO I HIRE?

30:42.509 --> 30:46.379
ALL THIS INTEREST?
I ASKED YOU ONE SIMPLE QUESTION.

30:46.379 --> 30:47.848
I WOULD APPRECIATE
IF YOU ANSWER IT.

30:47.848 --> 30:50.551
NO, JIM. I KNOW YOU.

30:50.551 --> 30:53.754
YOU DON'T SHOOT
UNLESS THERE'S A DEER.

30:53.754 --> 30:55.021
WHAT IS IT?

30:55.021 --> 30:58.291
YOU THINK YOU KNOW ME
PRETTY WELL, DON'T YOU?

30:58.291 --> 30:59.760
I SURE DO.

30:59.760 --> 31:01.535
HMM.

31:01.535 --> 31:05.338
WELL, I KNOW YOU PRETTY WELL,
TOO.

31:05.338 --> 31:07.473
REALLY?

31:07.473 --> 31:09.242
YES.
YOU SEE, WHAT YOU DO

31:09.242 --> 31:10.844
IS YOU GET ATTACHED
TO THESE PEOPLE,

31:10.844 --> 31:13.880
AND THEN THESE PEOPLE
BECOME PROBLEMS.

31:13.880 --> 31:16.449
I'M TELLING YOU, YOU ARE GETTING
TOO CLOSE TO THIS WOMAN.

31:16.449 --> 31:20.687
DON'T YOU TELL ME
WHO I AM GETTING CLOSE TO.

31:20.687 --> 31:22.723
AND DON'T YOU "DON'T" ME.

31:22.723 --> 31:24.891
SHE IS GOING TO
BE A PROBLEM.

31:24.891 --> 31:28.394
WELL, I LOOK FORWARD TO IT,
JIM.

31:28.394 --> 31:32.032
IT'LL BE ONE MORE PROBLEM I HAVE
TO DEAL WITH IN THIS FAMILY.

31:35.035 --> 31:37.103
GOOD NIGHT.

31:46.647 --> 31:52.285
♪♪♪♪

31:52.285 --> 31:58.058
♪♪♪♪

31:58.058 --> 31:59.526
HEY.

31:59.526 --> 32:02.202
HI.

32:02.202 --> 32:05.205
COME ON IN.

32:05.205 --> 32:07.240
OKAY.

32:12.245 --> 32:14.480
THANK YOU FOR COMING.

32:14.480 --> 32:17.584
SURE.

32:17.584 --> 32:19.620
HAVE A SEAT.

32:27.427 --> 32:30.664
CANDACE,
I'M SORRY FOR HITTING YOU.

32:30.664 --> 32:33.399
IT'S FINE.

32:33.399 --> 32:36.803
I WAS JUST REALLY UPSET.

32:36.803 --> 32:38.304
I AM, TOO.

32:38.304 --> 32:40.807
YOU ARE?

32:40.807 --> 32:42.175
YES.

32:42.175 --> 32:44.778
WHAT ARE YOU
UPSET ABOUT?

32:44.778 --> 32:45.946
ARE ‐‐
ARE YOU SERIOUS?

32:45.946 --> 32:49.616
YES.
I REALLY WANT TO KNOW.

32:49.616 --> 32:52.619
BENNY IN JAIL.

32:52.619 --> 32:54.254
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

32:54.254 --> 32:57.157
I DIDN'T CALL YOU UP HERE
TO ARGUE WITH YOU, CANDACE,

32:57.157 --> 33:01.935
BUT I REALIZE I CAN'T ASSUME
ANYTHING WITH YOU.

33:01.935 --> 33:06.339
I HAVE TO ASK.

33:06.339 --> 33:10.043
BENNY'S MY BROTHER.

33:10.043 --> 33:12.618
HE'S THE ONLY FAMILY
WHO LOVES ME.

33:16.149 --> 33:19.886
YOU DON'T HAVE TO SAY IT,
SO STOP THINKING ABOUT IT.

33:19.886 --> 33:21.955
THINKING ABOUT WHAT?

33:21.955 --> 33:25.854
HOW TO SAY YOU LOVE ME
AND MAKE IT SOUND REAL.

33:28.862 --> 33:32.065
I DO LOVE YOU.

33:32.065 --> 33:35.368
BUT I CAN'T SAY
I REALLY LIKE YOU RIGHT NOW,

33:35.368 --> 33:39.573
AND I SWEAR
I CAN'T STAND YOUR WAYS.

33:39.573 --> 33:43.476
THAT MAKES TWO OF US.

33:43.476 --> 33:45.411
THEN CHANGE.

33:45.411 --> 33:47.413
YOU FIRST.

33:47.413 --> 33:52.719
♪♪♪♪

33:52.719 --> 33:55.121
I WASN'T TALKING ABOUT
MY WAYS.

33:55.121 --> 33:56.422
I WAS TALKING ABOUT YOURS.

33:56.422 --> 33:58.158
MM.

33:58.158 --> 33:59.693
MY WAYS?

33:59.693 --> 34:02.302
YES.

34:02.302 --> 34:04.538
YOUR WAYS.

34:04.538 --> 34:09.009
I LIVE FOR THE LORD.

34:09.009 --> 34:12.746
WELL, IF YOU LIVE FOR THE LORD,
THEN YOU JUST DO IT.

34:12.746 --> 34:15.015
YOU DON'T GO AROUND
TRYING TO SHOW EVERYBODY

34:15.015 --> 34:17.884
THAT YOU HAVE A BIBLE.

34:17.884 --> 34:21.522
WHAT, YOU THINK THAT'S GONNA
HIDE WHO YOU REALLY ARE?

34:21.522 --> 34:25.626
WHO DO YOU REALLY THINK
I REALLY AM?

34:25.626 --> 34:29.462
I DON'T THINK.
I KNOW.

34:29.462 --> 34:32.833
OKAY.

34:32.833 --> 34:35.536
WHO DO YOU KNOW I AM?

34:39.239 --> 34:45.879
I KNOW THAT MY FATHER WAS
A ONE‐NIGHT STAND.

34:45.879 --> 34:48.549
YOU MET HIM AT A CLUB.

34:48.549 --> 34:51.151
HE WAS A BARTENDER.

34:51.151 --> 34:55.321
AND BENNY'S FATHER ‐‐
HE WAS MARRIED,

34:55.321 --> 34:58.358
AND YOU TRIED TO STEAL HIM
FROM HIS WIFE,

34:58.358 --> 35:00.827
BUT HE WOULDN'T GO...

35:00.827 --> 35:07.574
AND THE SLEW OF OTHER MARRIED
MEN THAT YOU SLEPT WITH.

35:12.212 --> 35:16.883
SOME OF THAT'S TRUE.

35:16.883 --> 35:20.854
NOT ALL OF IT.

35:20.854 --> 35:24.457
BUT I ASKED GOD
TO FORGIVE ME.

35:24.457 --> 35:25.859
OF COURSE.

35:25.859 --> 35:28.862
SEE, I REPENTED.

35:28.862 --> 35:32.799
AND THAT'S WHAT THE TRUE MEANING
OF REPENTANCE IS ‐‐

35:32.799 --> 35:36.570
WHEN YOU INTEND
WITH ALL YOUR HEART

35:36.570 --> 35:41.207
AND YOUR SOUL AND YOUR MIND
NOT TO DO IT AGAIN.

35:41.207 --> 35:44.878
BUT SEE, YOU ‐‐
YOU DON'T REPENT.

35:44.878 --> 35:50.116
YOU INTEND TO DO THIS
OVER AND OVER AND OVER AGAIN.

35:50.116 --> 35:52.452
SEE, THAT'S WHAT YOU'VE BEEN
DOING SINCE YOU WAS 7 YEARS OLD,

35:52.452 --> 35:56.923
WHEN YOU FIRST
STARTED STEALING.

35:56.923 --> 36:02.268
WHEN YOU WERE 13, YOU STOLE MY
MORTGAGE MONEY TO BUY A COMPUTER

36:02.268 --> 36:04.571
AND SOME SHOES
AND A DRESS,

36:04.571 --> 36:08.542
AND YOU LIED TO ME
AND SAID YOU DIDN'T DO IT,

36:08.542 --> 36:13.814
JUST SO YOU COULD
FIT IN AT SCHOOL.

36:13.814 --> 36:16.082
THEN,
WHEN YOU WERE 17 YEARS OLD,

36:16.082 --> 36:20.921
YOU RAN AWAY TO SHACK UP WITH
SOME PIMP IN MEMPHIS,

36:20.921 --> 36:24.324
AND YOU CALLED ME,
CRYING.

36:24.324 --> 36:27.628
I TOOK THE BUS DOWN THERE
TO GET YOU,

36:27.628 --> 36:31.497
BROUGHT YOU BACK HOME WHEN
HE THREATENED TO KILL YOU,

36:31.497 --> 36:36.002
BROUGHT YOU HOME UNDER THE
THREAT THAT HE'D KILL ALL OF US.

36:36.002 --> 36:38.505
I WORRIED ABOUT THAT
EVERY DAY,

36:38.505 --> 36:42.809
TILL SOMEBODY ENDED UP
KILLING HIM.

36:42.809 --> 36:46.112
THEN YOU GOT PREGNANT.

36:46.112 --> 36:49.382
HAD THAT BEAUTIFUL BABY ‐‐

36:49.382 --> 36:53.486
MY GRANDBABY, THAT YOU LET ME
RAISE AND LOVE.

36:53.486 --> 36:55.522
AND I LOVED THAT BABY.

36:59.793 --> 37:01.835
THREE YEARS
THAT BABY WAS HERE.

37:05.304 --> 37:07.741
AND THEN YOU TOOK HIM.

37:07.741 --> 37:09.776
I AIN'T SEEN HIM SINCE.

37:14.380 --> 37:16.750
[ CHUCKLES ]

37:16.750 --> 37:20.621
OKAY,
WHAT AM I DOING HERE?

37:20.621 --> 37:24.457
WHY ‐‐ WHY AM I HERE?

37:24.457 --> 37:27.528
PLEASE, PLEASE.

37:27.528 --> 37:33.700
I BEG OF YOU, DO THE RIGHT THING
FOR ONCE IN YOUR LIFE.

37:33.700 --> 37:35.301
TELL THEM PEOPLE THE TRUTH

37:35.301 --> 37:39.606
SO YOUR BROTHER
CAN GET OUT OF JAIL.

37:39.606 --> 37:42.743
SO YOU CALLED ME OVER HERE SO
I COULD TAKE HIS PLACE IN JAIL?

37:42.743 --> 37:46.647
I CALLED YOU OVER HERE
TO DO THE RIGHT THING.

37:46.647 --> 37:50.150
YOU CALLED ME OVER HERE
SO THAT I CAN GO IN

37:50.150 --> 37:52.953
AND TAKE THE FALL
FOR YOUR GOLDEN BOY.

37:52.953 --> 37:56.690
CANDACE,
YOU NEED TO FIX THIS.

37:56.690 --> 37:58.592
HOW MANY TIMES
DO I HAVE TO TELL YOU

37:58.592 --> 38:01.902
I DIDN'T HAVE ANYTHING
TO DO WITH THIS?

38:01.902 --> 38:04.237
THEN WHO DID?

38:04.237 --> 38:06.006
MAMA,
THOSE DRUGS WEREN'T MINE.

38:06.006 --> 38:11.512
ANSWER THE QUESTION.

38:11.512 --> 38:13.714
OKAY,
I CAN'T DO THIS.

38:13.714 --> 38:15.315
NO, NO, PLEASE.

38:15.315 --> 38:18.218
PLEASE, CANDACE,
SIT DOWN.

38:18.218 --> 38:21.522
PLEASE,
JUST TELL THE TRUTH!

38:21.522 --> 38:23.557
I AM.
I'M OUT OF HERE.

38:27.427 --> 38:31.297
CANDACE...

38:31.297 --> 38:34.601
THERE'S A LOT TO FORGIVE YOU
FOR, DAUGHTER.

38:34.601 --> 38:39.005
♪♪♪♪

38:40.040 --> 38:43.710
AND I THINK I JUST RUN OUT OF
ROOM FOR IT.

38:43.710 --> 38:50.450
♪♪♪♪

38:50.450 --> 38:53.654
IF YOU DON'T
HELP YOUR BROTHER...

38:57.457 --> 38:59.492
YOU'RE DEAD TO ME.

39:03.169 --> 39:06.973
GREAT.

39:06.973 --> 39:10.110
GREAT.

39:10.110 --> 39:14.480
THAT'S WHAT
YOU WANTED ANYWAY.

39:14.480 --> 39:16.482
IT'S WHAT YOU ALWAYS WANTED.

39:16.482 --> 39:22.222
♪♪♪♪

39:22.222 --> 39:26.960
YOU ALWAYS
MADE ME FEEL LIKE

39:26.960 --> 39:31.331
YOU'D RATHER ME BE DEAD.

39:31.331 --> 39:35.001
NOW YOU SAID IT.

39:35.001 --> 39:39.272
YOU SAID IT.

39:39.272 --> 39:41.508
OKAY.

39:41.508 --> 39:46.112
YOU THINK
I'M THE DEVIL?

39:46.112 --> 39:49.650
YOU HAVE NO IDEA
OF THE HELL I CAN RAIN DOWN.

39:49.650 --> 39:56.690
♪♪♪♪

39:56.690 --> 40:03.704
♪♪♪♪

40:03.704 --> 40:05.706
[ POUNDING AT DOOR ]

40:05.706 --> 40:09.976
♪♪♪♪

40:09.976 --> 40:11.578
WHAT THE HELL IS THAT?

40:11.578 --> 40:13.580
[ POUNDING CONTINUES ]

40:13.580 --> 40:19.586
♪♪♪♪

40:19.586 --> 40:21.221
CANDACE? WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU DOING HERE?

40:21.221 --> 40:22.956
‐YOU SET ME UP.
‐NO, NO!

40:22.956 --> 40:24.925
YES, YOU DID.
YOU SET ME UP.

40:24.925 --> 40:26.492
NO, I DIDN'T!
BUT YOU KEEP YOUR VOICE DOWN!

40:26.492 --> 40:28.795
‐I DON'T GIVE A DAMN!
‐CANDACE, STOP IT!

40:28.795 --> 40:30.096
YOU BROUGHT THIS
ON YOURSELF.

40:30.096 --> 40:32.599
YOU WANT A WAR?
HERE IT IS.

40:32.599 --> 40:35.536
NO! YOU'RE NOT GOING UP
THE DAMN STAIRS!

40:35.536 --> 40:37.037
YOU LISTEN TO ME.

40:37.037 --> 40:39.339
YOU BOUGHT THAT CAR
TO SET ME UP, RIGHT?

40:39.339 --> 40:40.741
YOU DON'T GET IT.

40:40.741 --> 40:42.242
I WILL RUIN YOU!

40:42.242 --> 40:43.677
NO.
I DIDN'T DO IT.

40:43.677 --> 40:45.045
I DIDN'T HAVE ANYTHING
TO DO WITH IT.

40:45.045 --> 40:48.148
MY BROTHER IS IN JAIL BECAUSE OF
YOU, SO LET'S MAKE THIS EVEN.

40:48.148 --> 40:50.116
‐NO! CAN‐‐
‐GET OFF OF ME!

40:50.116 --> 40:51.785
CANDACE!

40:51.785 --> 40:52.786
GET DOWN HERE!

40:52.786 --> 40:53.954
YOU'RE NOT GOING ‐‐

40:53.954 --> 40:57.558
GET OFF OF ME!

40:57.558 --> 40:58.692
KATHERYN!

40:58.692 --> 40:59.726
CANDACE!

40:59.726 --> 41:00.967
‐GET OFF OF ME!
‐CANDACE!

41:00.967 --> 41:03.670
GET OFF OF ME!
KATHERYN!

41:03.670 --> 41:09.610
♪♪♪♪

41:09.610 --> 41:12.513
WHAT IS GOING ON?!

41:12.513 --> 41:16.683
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:16.683 --> 41:18.451
I HAVE SOMETHING
TO TELL YOU.

41:18.451 --> 41:19.853
[ Voice breaking ]
PLEASE, LORD, PLEASE!

41:19.853 --> 41:21.154
PLEASE JUST HELP MY CHILD!

41:21.154 --> 41:23.924
I'LL CALL YOU AS SOON AS
I HEAR FROM AN ATTORNEY.

41:23.924 --> 41:26.593
OKAY.

41:26.593 --> 41:28.595
YOU HAD YOUR VISITOR.

41:28.595 --> 41:29.596
I HAD MINE.

41:29.596 --> 41:30.631
IT'S YOUR MESS.

41:30.631 --> 41:32.566
THAT YOU CREATED,
BY THE WAY.

41:32.566 --> 41:35.301
I DID NOT TELL YOU
TO FRAME ANYONE.

41:35.301 --> 41:38.071
CAN'T GET IN IT WITHOUT
GETTING MY HANDS DIRTY.

41:38.071 --> 41:40.106
YOUR HANDS ARE PLENTY DIRTY
ALREADY.

41:40.106 --> 41:45.445
DO YOU WANT ANOTHER ONE,
DIAPER BOY, HMM?

41:45.445 --> 41:46.713
OH.

41:46.713 --> 41:47.848
STILL GONNA RUN?

41:47.848 --> 41:48.849
WHY WOULDN'T I?

41:48.849 --> 41:50.751
I DON'T KNOW.

41:50.751 --> 41:52.118
I THOUGHT
MAYBE YOU'D BE WORRIED

41:52.118 --> 41:54.320
THAT ONE OF YOUR CHRONOLOGICALS
WOULD GO PUBLIC.

41:54.320 --> 41:56.623
I HATE THE WAY
HOSPITALS SMELL.

41:56.623 --> 41:58.124
IT'S OKAY TO BE SCARED.

41:58.124 --> 42:00.333
GOOD, 'CAUSE I AM.

42:02.168 --> 42:03.937
AMANDA.

42:03.937 --> 42:05.906
AMANDA!
